Package: Rtts
Type: Package
Title: Convert Text into Speech
Depends: RCurl
Version: 0.3.0
Date: 2015-05-30
Author: Xiaodong Deng
Maintainer: Xiaodong Deng <xd_deng@hotmail.com>
Description: Convert text into speech (voice file in mp3 or wav format) with APIs offered by Google Translate and ITRI TTS. Two main functions are given corresponding these two APIS, tts_google() and tts_ITRI(). For tts_google(), only English is supported. For tts_ITRI(), English and Chinese (both traditional and simplified) are supported, and user can specify the speaker accent, speed and volume. Both functions require internet connecion.
URL: http://r-text-2-speech.r-forge.r-project.org/
License: GPL-3
LazyData: TRUE
NeedsCompilation: no
